00:22:50.050 --> 00:22:54.783
and I've often wondered if Obama who
grew up in this multiracial society

00:22:55.300 --> 00:22:59.500
in Hawaii, had international
exposure can he possibly understand

00:23:01.720 --> 00:23:04.720
the vitriol of southern
white anger toward him

00:23:05.710 --> 00:23:08.243
as I can having come
from that culture.

00:23:09.310 --> 00:23:10.610
&gt;&gt; You know I'm not a novelist
and when I say I'm not--

00:23:11.610 --> 00:23:15.743
what I mean by that is a novelist
because here she is making it

00:23:16.010 --> 00:23:19.143
up can go as deep as that
imagination can reach.

00:23:20.210 --> 00:23:24.743
I think no biographer or journalist
can pretend to reach that deeply.

00:23:26.180 --> 00:23:26.930
Certainly Obama has read widely in
the history of race, in the history

00:23:30.030 --> 00:23:33.630
of civil rights, he knows
these things from a distance,

00:23:35.300 --> 00:23:36.043
he is also a black man in America
and has felt the sting of prejudice

00:23:39.090 --> 00:23:42.623
as well as any black man or
woman has sooner or later,

00:23:42.860 --> 00:23:45.993
no one escapes uninjured
in some way or another.

00:23:46.640 --> 00:23:46.680
