try to get inside a piece enough

00:26:48.090 --> 00:26:48.476
and it happens through a long
relationship with the writer,

00:26:51.570 --> 00:26:56.236
to make that thing better, to find--
to help in whether it's structural

00:26:58.720 --> 00:27:02.986
or intellectual or word by word
to make as beautiful and as clear

00:27:07.160 --> 00:27:09.893
and as forceful a piece
of writing can be.

00:27:10.600 --> 00:27:11.486
So, and all people do it in
different ways and it has to do

00:27:13.580 --> 00:27:14.180
with an extension of
their personalities

00:27:15.580 --> 00:27:16.313
and the intellect they
bring to the table.

00:27:17.580 --> 00:27:17.586
